      <p>
        Now use interval notation to express where <m>x^2-6x+5 \gt 0</m>.
        <ol marker="A." cols="2">
            <li><m>(\infty, 1] \cup [5, \infty)</m></li>
            <li><m>[1,5]</m></li>
            <li><m>(\infty, 1) \cup (5, \infty)</m></li>
